metadata.dc:description: Contribution of one case of supernumerary kidney with ureter ectopically opened to vagina associated to horseshoe kidney. Supernumerary kidneys are extremely unusual entities, there being only about 70 cases described in the international literature. This is the first case where it is found associated to horseshoe kidney.
metadata.dc:title: Riñón supernumerario con abocamiento de uréter ectópico a vagina asociado a riñón en herradura.
[Supernumerary kidney with ectopic ureteral opening to the vagina associated with horseshoe kidney].
